<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Giglet" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Giglet</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Giglot,</orth> 1) subst. a lewd woman, a wanton: <bibl n="shak. mm 5.352" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 352</bibl>.<lb />2) adj.: <cit><quote>a g. wench,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.7.41" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 7, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>g. fortune,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 1, 31</bibl></cit> [== "fickle, inconstant", Wyatt, Warwick Sh.]
